sources.description:
True Justice: *Angel of Death* - Kane and his team track two suitcase nukes that have been smuggled into the country – and Kane thinks the Ghost is working to buy them. As Kane gets ever-closer to The Ghost, the stakes continue to rise.
2010.  Stars: Steven Seagal, Sarah Lind, William 'Big Sleeps' Stewart, Meghan Ory, Warren Christie
